# Kecktech IT — Cursor Project Rules
# Last updated: 2026-04-29

## Identity
Company: Kecktech IT Solutions LLC — family-owned, disability-led, solar-powered IT services, Park City, Kansas
Operator: Jon Keck (GitHub: Bizzo1975)
Launch date: 2026-05-12
Primary domain: kecktech.net

## This Repo — kecktech-dashboard
- website/src/data/ — JSON content files — THIS is where page content lives
- website/src/components/ — Astro components
- website/dist/ — Built output served by nginx (do not edit directly)
- website/nginx/nginx.conf — nginx config for kecktech-web container

Build command: cd /opt/docker/dashboard/website && npm run build
Run after every content or component change.

## Branch Strategy
dev → VMID 730 (dev-dashboard-01, 10.30.0.143) → https://dev.kecktech.net
main → VMID 230 (prod-dashboard-01, 10.20.0.143) → https://kecktech.net
Never commit directly to main.

After any file edit:
  cd /opt/docker/dashboard/website
  npm run build
  git add .
  git commit -m "your message"
  git push origin dev

