## Homepage Rule
Senior Concierge intentionally hidden from homepage cards.
Shows on /services and /pricing only. 3 cards on homepage.

## services.json — available flag
Each service has "available": true or false.
Only available:true entries are rendered on client pages.
Deferred services stay in file with available:false.

## Content File Map
src/data/home.json → homepage
src/data/services.json → /services page
src/data/pricing.json → /pricing page
src/data/contact.json → /contact page
src/data/about.json → /about page
src/data/global.json → footer (all pages)
src/components/ContactForm.astro → contact form (service dropdown hardcoded here)

## Non-Negotiables
- No pricing changes without operator confirmation
- No deferred services on client-facing pages
- Never commit to main directly
- Run npm run build after every content change
- jacob-roman.com is anonymous — never associate with Jon Keck or Kecktech

